posts.title: The Shawshank Redemption
posts.description: Two imprisoned men bond over a number of years, finding solace and eventual redemption through acts of common decency.

posts.title: The Godfather
posts.description: The aging patriarch of an organized crime dynasty in postwar New York City transfers control of his clandestine empire to his reluctant youngest son.

posts.title: Rocky Balboa
posts.description: Thirty years after the ring of the first bell, Rocky Balboa comes out of retirement and dons his gloves for his final fight against the reigning heavyweight champ Mason 'The Line' Dixon.

posts.title: Wednesday
posts.description: Follows Wednesday Addams' years as a student, when she attempts to master her emerging psychic ability, thwart and solve the mystery that embroiled her parents.
